{\an8}<i>WOMAN: ♪ Yeah, yeah, you ♪</i>

23:04.382 --> 23:08.637
{\an8}<i>♪ Just gotta let it loose ♪</i>

23:08.720 --> 23:12.432
{\an8}<i>♪ And do what you</i>
<i>choose to do ♪</i>

23:12.516 --> 23:15.185
{\an8}<i>♪ Don't walk away ♪</i>

23:15.268 --> 23:17.229
{\an8}<i>♪ Yeah, yeah ♪</i>

23:17.312 --> 23:19.189
{\an8}<i>♪ If you want to play ♪</i>

23:19.272 --> 23:21.316
{\an8}<i>♪ Come and play today ♪</i>

23:21.399 --> 23:24.486
{\an8}<i>♪ Let's just get away ♪</i>

